  "name": "A custom-made AAV1 variant (AAV1-T593K) enables efficient transduction of Japanese quail neurons in vitro and in vivo",
  "author": {
    "name": "Shai Berlin",
    "givenName": "Shai",
    "familyName": "Berlin",
